half as fun without you in it.

41:49.811 --> 41:50.899
Be careful.

41:54.294 --> 41:56.383
I love you too, Murphy.

41:58.733 --> 42:00.779
God, keep them safe.

42:13.922 --> 42:17.926
What do you think? Maybe
you want to say a few words?

42:22.714 --> 42:25.020
Actions speak louder than words.
